<section id="Cosulta"  class="bg-[#D4BDA4] py-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#5A2E1B] text-center mb-8">Contactanos</h2>
    <p class="text-[#5A2E1B] text-center mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      ¿Tienes alguna consulta o sugerencia? ¡Nos encantaría escucharte! Completa el siguiente formulario y nos pondremos en contacto contigo lo antes posible.
    </p>
    <form class="bg-[#E7D2B9] rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 max-w-md mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-6">
        <label for="name" class="block text-[#5A2E1B] font-semibold mb-2">Nombre</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="name"
          name="name"
          placeholder="Ingresa tu nombre"
          class="w-full border border-[#5A2E1B] bg-[#F3E5D8] rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8A5A44]"
          required
        />
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <label for="email" class="block text-[#5A2E1B] font-semibold mb-2">Email</label>
        <input
          type="email"
          id="email"
          name="email"
          placeholder="Ingresa tu email"
          class="w-full border border-[#5A2E1B] bg-[#F3E5D8] rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8A5A44]"
          required
        />
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <label for="subject" class="block text-[#5A2E1B] font-semibold mb-2">Asunto</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="subject"
          name="subject"
          placeholder="Escribe el asunto"
          class="w-full border border-[#5A2E1B] bg-[#F3E5D8] rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8A5A44]"
          required
        />
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <label for="message" class="block text-[#5A2E1B] font-semibold mb-2">Mensaje</label>
        <textarea
          id="message"
          name="message"
          rows="4"
          placeholder="Ingresa tu mensaje"
          class="w-full border border-[#5A2E1B] bg-[#F3E5D8] rounded-lg px-4 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8A5A44]"
          required
        ></textarea>
      </div>
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full bg-[#5A2E1B] hover:bg-[#3D1F12] text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg transition duration-300"
      >
        Enviar
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>